Studio Ghibli style illustration of a whimsical workshop scene where a craftsperson assembles intricate wooden puzzle boxes and modular components on a worn wooden workbench. Each small box glows softly with different warm colors—amber, rose, and soft blue—representing reusable building blocks. The boxes stack and connect in satisfying ways, some open to reveal smaller nested pieces inside. Scattered around are tiny tools, measuring instruments, and sketches of component designs. Through a large arched window, late afternoon golden sunlight streams in, casting long shadows. A curious spirit-like creature made of translucent geometric shapes watches from a shelf above, surrounded by jars containing glowing modular pieces waiting to be assembled. The atmosphere is one of careful craftsmanship, patient preparation, and the joy of building something elegant from well-designed parts.
